Smoke-test cases in the check target:
-------------------------------------
stdCopyTest- checks if the program works with no options
fdRedirectionTest- checks if the program works using the file descriptor redirection
segmentationTest- checks the --segfault option
catchTest- checks the --catch option
invalidOptionsTest- checks for the correct exit status when an invalid option is given